data.description: Welcome home to this charming and spacious 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom ranch style single family home! Situated in a peaceful neighborhood, this property offers the perfect blend of comfort and accessibility, boasting a 1 car garage and a convenient handicap accessible ramp for ease of entry. Home is currently being freshly painted, new counter tops installed, fascia replaced and new flooring in laundry room. Refrigerator, Dishwasher, Range, Security Camera's and Handicap Ramp convey! Sellers are paying $4,000.00 carpet allowance and $2,000.00 for exterior paint/closing costs.
